  presence if 15.11.=N then optional else blocked
  help     "This is the reason that pediatrics services are not available.  It can be set only when \"Pediatrics: Available Now\" is \"No\"."
  pdf      text P 2 L 292.72 R 479.20 B 225.20 T 243.28 BL 230.16

field 15.11d.
